-- Online gaming firm Bwin.Party considering sale - Bloomberg
-- By Karen Rebelo in Bangalore
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 12:47AM EDT
-- None



June 26 (Reuters) - Online gambling company Bwin.Party Digital Entertainment Plc <BPTY.L> is considering selling itself or part of the company as part of a strategic review, Bloomberg reported on Thursday citing two sources.

Bwin.Party hired Deutsche Bank to consider its options, Bloomberg said citing two people with knowledge of the matter. (http://bloom.bg/TyOVa0) The company is expected to decide within two months, according to one source, Bloomberg said.